00225 void Lgm_Nutation( double T_TT, double nTerms, double *dPsi, double *dEps ) {
00226 
00227     int     i;
00228     double  Mmoon, Msun, uMmoon, Dsun, Nmoon;
00229     double  ap, PsiSum, EpsSum, T2_TT, T3_TT;
00230 
00231     T2_TT = T_TT*T_TT; T3_TT = T2_TT*T_TT;
00232     Mmoon  = fmod( 134.96340251 + (1325.0*360.0 + 198.8675605)*T_TT + 0.0088553*T2_TT + 1.4343e-5*T3_TT, 360.0)*RadPerDeg;
00233     Msun   = fmod( 357.52910918 + (99.0*360.0   + 359.0502911)*T_TT - 0.0001537*T2_TT +    3.8e-8*T3_TT, 360.0)*RadPerDeg;
00234     uMmoon = fmod(  93.27209062 + (1342.0*360.0 +  82.0174577)*T_TT - 0.0035420*T2_TT -   2.88e-7*T3_TT, 360.0)*RadPerDeg;
00235     Dsun   = fmod( 297.85019547 + (1236.0*360.0 + 307.1114469)*T_TT - 0.0017696*T2_TT +  1.831e-6*T3_TT, 360.0)*RadPerDeg;
00236     Nmoon  = fmod( 125.04455501 - (5.0*360.0    + 134.1361851)*T_TT + 0.0020756*T2_TT +  2.139e-6*T3_TT, 360.0)*RadPerDeg;
00237 
00238     if (nTerms > 106) nTerms = 106;
00239     for (PsiSum = EpsSum = 0.0, i=0; i<nTerms; i++){
00240 
00241         ap = a[i][0]*Mmoon + a[i][1]*Msun + a[i][2]*uMmoon + a[i][3]*Dsun + a[i][4]*Nmoon;
00242         PsiSum += (A[i][0] + 0.1*A[i][1]*T_TT)*sin( ap );
00243         EpsSum += (A[i][2] + 0.1*A[i][3]*T_TT)*cos( ap );
00244 
00245     }
00246 
00247     *dPsi = PsiSum*0.0001;
00248     *dEps = EpsSum*0.0001;
